media:group.media:title: Steelseries Apex M800 review (QS1 switches)
media:group.media:description:
Skip to 10:29 for a typing demonstration. 
Today we look at the Steelseries Apex M800, a kind of semi-old RGB-focused battlecruiser keyboard from the mid-2010s. Hope you enjoy the video! :)

The practice sentence was: "Hello my name is Thomas and I'm typing on a Steelseries Apex M800 right now. It's not the worst I've ever reviewed, but I'm just wishing it was an Apex Pro instead!"
